	(text "AC coupling would be nice - but do I need to add an optional buffer to the input curcuitry\nthis opAmp/buffer circuit prevents AC coupling LPF form having its fc modified by downstream circuitry\nhigh GBWP op amp ideal switchable input gain/attenuation may be ideal e.g. /100, x1, x100 or maybe /10, x1, x10, x100"
